I need to identify the tax accrued but not yet paid from the balance sheet.

Looking at the balance sheet, the line item that represents tax accrued but not yet paid would be "Taxes Payable". This represents taxes that have been incurred but haven't yet been paid to the relevant tax authorities.

From the balance sheet provided:
- Initial value of Taxes Payable: 0.00 (as of 2023-12-31)
- End value of Taxes Payable: 43168.61 (as of 2024-02-01)

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '0.00', 'end value': '43168.61'}}
```
